 <text pwt="true"><style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true" pwt="true">Note: this page is ported from MCMOD's GTCEu wiki.<br/>Author: <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/179043/">花海</style>, <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/119280/">Oganesson897</style><br/></style></text>
